---
import SocialList from "@/components/SocialList.astro";
---

<section class="hero-board">
	<div class="hero-board__main">
		<div class="hero-board__meta">
			<span class="hero-board__stamp" aria-hidden="true">OPEN</span>
			<span class="hero-board__comment">// 今日营业中 · 招待散客</span>
		</div>
		<h1 class="hero-board__title">
			嘿，欢迎来到我的小饭桌 <span class="hero-board__emoji">🍚</span>
		</h1>
		<p class="hero-board__line">
			这是我的博客，本来想叫「菜谱」「菜单」，听着像正经餐厅太端着，最后选了「小饭桌」——支张桌、摆几道菜，谁路过都能坐，扒两口就走也行。
		</p>
		<p class="hero-board__line">
			桌上端的都是自己做的：写的代码、追的源码、折腾的小工具，外加一堆没啥用但挺好玩的念头。有的是大菜配图配流程图，有的就一口炸鸡
			<span class="hero-board__emoji">🍗</span> 看心情上。
		</p>
		<div class="hero-board__cta">
			<a class="btn btn--primary" href="/posts/">去看看文章</a>
			<a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/about/">关于我</a>
		</div>
		<div class="hero-board__social"><SocialList /></div>
	</div>

	<aside class="hero-board__menu" aria-hidden="true">
		<img
			alt=""
			class="hero-board__scene"
			height={1024}
			loading="eager"
			src="/illustrations/hero-scene.png"
			width={1536}
		/>
	</aside>
</section>
